LTD "EJ Baltic" is a modern wood processing company that performs all wood processing works. We try to be a good and reliable partner for our customers, we strive for long-term cooperation and we offer the highest quality wood at the most attractive price.
Our company provides a wide range of services:
•	sawing with band-saw blade and multi-saw machines;
•	Splitting;
•	planing;
•	Drying;
•	Impregnation;
•	CNC milling.
We also produce and sell structural (calibrated) wood for frame house structures, roofs, scaffolding, formwork, fences, etc.
In addition, we produce interior paneling, terrace and floor boards.
The main suppliers of wood are the Scandinavian countries, so we offer our customers only high-quality Nordic wood.
Those wishing to purchase wood products are invited to visit www.ejbaltic.lt or come to our shopping terminal located in Valkos st. 7, Vydeniai village, Varėnas district.
